The paper discusses deep artificial neural networks and their applications in pattern recognition and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also covers supervised and unsupervised learning, which are common topics in cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and natural language processing (cs.CL) as areas where deep learning has been successful.
